# Capacitor native folders (added when platform is added)
# We keep these ignored or committed depending on preference.
# Usually native folders are committed in Capacitor projects, but we'll let the user decide.
# We'll ignore the local gradle config files and output APKs.
android/.gradle/
android/local.properties
android/app/build/
android/app/src/main/assets/public/
